ezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Queen of the Gods whispers to Hippolyte</span><hr size=1> :::Arahuta had woken in the middle of a misty field. The shamaness stood up quickly and looked around.  Suddenly, she was hit with a blast in the middle of her back that threw her far and then down into a muddy pit.  Ara pushed herself slowely up out of the mud and then turned her head to see a woman dressed in black with an evil smile upon her face. <br>
