Who are you and what do you want with me?<br>
The woman laughed, &quot;No one told you about the great and powerful Alti?  What fools.  Well, let me introduce myself, I am Alti the most powerful shamaness there ever was or will be.&quot; :::Suddenly, Ara felt a shock again, where Alti's foot touched her stomach.  Tears began to show in Ara's eyes. &quot;Oh, what a weakling of a shamaness the amazons have found now,&quot; Alti laughed. <p>::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::~~::
