Cursed Hades, can't you even control your own Dead!!!!!!!<br>
:::Hipp's face looked grim.  The feather began to turn a dark grey and Hippolyte sighed.  Slowely, she pulled out her scimitar...believing she was about to have to kill her new friend, for the sake of Alysia's child.::: <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
